{"tid":1477855,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】國泰CEO何杲已離職","createTime":"2019-08-16T09:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T10:05:47.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"221f38863f41f48af039b2660cd59453ad2299cc","tid":1477855,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3168390/org/6d1a9fd158ebaaac1f8dcf3649c345c6.jpg/mtghcYffbsyY6nWrP9ZsSkcVM05a0bfABLsEowS7BKM?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3168390%2Forg%2F6d1a9fd158ebaaac1f8dcf3649c345c6.jpg%2FmtghcYffbsyY6nWrP9ZsSkcVM05a0bfABLsEowS7BKM%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=68431eaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《央視》報道，國泰航空（0293）宣布人事變動，已接受行政總裁何杲辭任，及盧家培辭任顧客及商務總裁職務。同時引由港機行政總裁鄧健榮，及林紹波兩人接任。<br />\n惟截至發稿，國泰網頁及香港交易所（0388）仍未見有公告。《香港01》向國泰進行查詢，但是電話無法接通。<br />\n8月9日，內地民航局向國泰發出重大安全風險警示。太古主席施銘倫到北京晤民航局後，中國民航局綜合司副司長顧曉紅在新聞發布會上表示，國泰航空按時報送飛往內地和飛往內地領空的機組人員身份信息，經審核，有關信息符合警示要求。<br />\n而此前，國泰早前亦宣布再解僱兩名機師，指兩人分別被控暴動罪和洩漏航班資料，公司又重申遵從所有營運司法管轄區監管機構的規定和指引。"},{"pid":"b36b9f128b1d0d0b5a751c17c8acba981917ee76","tid":1477855,"uid":182207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYFJD9D.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYFJD9D.gif&h=14e25730&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TMDbN2Y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTMDbN2Y.gif&h=096a141f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wv61qPD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWv61qPD.gif&h=b045936b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cjenagj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCjenagj.gif&h=c047c2b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78df526f6be8e0573f0446350ebfe26f694547ff","tid":1477855,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited